<section class="px-6 py-24 bg-canvas border-t border-hairline transition-colors duration-300">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-16 items-center">
    <div class="flex-1">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink mb-6">About ToolTails Word Counter</h2>
      <p class="text-body text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We built the ToolTails Word Counter to be the fastest, most private text analysis tool on the web. As writers and developers ourselves, we were tired of tools that stored our data or cluttered the screen with ads.
      </p>
      <p class="text-body text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Everything you type here is processed locally in your browser. It's safe, instantly responsive, and designed to help you hit your character limits and readability goals with zero friction.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-canvas-soft border border-hairline text-sm font-medium text-ink shadow-sm transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="18" height="11" x="3" y="11" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"></path></svg>
          100% Private
        </div>
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-canvas-soft border border-hairline text-sm font-medium text-ink shadow-sm transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2v20"></path><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"></path></svg>
          Always Free
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="w-full md:w-2/5 aspect-square bg-canvas-soft rounded-[2.5rem] border border-hairline shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden group transition-colors duration-300">
